title: Live event June 19 CS Lewis Society and Nevada City Meetup
description:
This coming week I'll be giving my second talk at the CS Lewis society of Northern California. We're also helping start a new meetup in Nevada City California. 

Location: CS Lewis Society of California
100 Swan Way, Oakland CA 94621
https://goo.gl/maps/c2Eye2nNs3tN2sUS6 

Recommended donation of $10 to cover refreshments. 

Sign up here https://www.eventbrite.com/e/12-rules-of-life-book-discussion-tickets-62536910583 

CS Lewis Society https://www.lewissociety.org
Future events Page https://www.lewissociety.org/future-events/#book-club
Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/lewissociety/

https://www.meetup.com/Nevada-City-Jordan-B-Peterson-Meetup-Group/events/261855916/
